channel.title: Giving level 80 RS acc. to anyone who does this for me!
channel.description:
[B]Well.. I know this is a ton, but I need someone experienced in Project Insanity to set me up a Project Insanity server.. I want Erased Pkz newest release. I will kinda customize the client to my liking then leave the source alone till we're done. I just need somebody to setup a server (and client of course) and make it into a jar and then finally a webclient. I have JarMaker, WinRaR, and a little experience in servers (I currently have a Delta, but I need someone else to set up my Project Insanity. And before you say "Get Experienced in it" , I have. I have set my own up just for me.. customized it for like a whole night.. and come to find out I cannot jar it, because I get error when I open it about not having main-class:class.
I will give my RS account for it, It has like 88 wc. 70 str. 60-something attk and def. Also has quite a bit of member stuff!!
Thanks to anyone in advance~!![/B]
